S'Figure 3b: Left panel, frequency distribution of sequence modifications that increase read length with respect to the reference amplicon, classified as insertions (positive indel size). Middle panel, frequency distribution of sequence modifications that reduce read length with respect to the reference amplicon, classified as deletions (negative indel size). Right panel, frequency distribution of sequence modifications that do not alter read length with respect to the reference amplicon, which are classified as substitutions (number of substituted positions shown).'
